Author: glugglugbiggulp
Text: The doctor I worked with yesterday said I’m ”small and cute now”. She’s a woman and I’m a woman too so it wasn’t like she was hitting on me or anything, but it was weird... I just usually pat my flabby ass stomach and say thanks for the compliment. But small.... really..... how dare you lie to my face...

Author: AngeloLacrime
Text: 🙄 Yep. My SIL telling me I'm looking skinny even though I'm definitely not. Like can you not lie to me? I know you're trying to be nice, but don't.
